31#ifndef _OPENSOLARIS_SYS_SDT_H_
32#define _OPENSOLARIS_SYS_SDT_H_
33
34#include_next <sys/sdt.h>
35#include <sys/dtrace.h>
36
37#undef DTRACE_PROBE
38#undef DTRACE_PROBE1
39#undef DTRACE_PROBE2
40#undef DTRACE_PROBE3
41#undef DTRACE_PROBE4
42#undef DTRACE_PROBE5
43#undef DTRACE_PROBE6
44#undef DTRACE_PROBE7
45
46#define DTRACE_PROBE(name)
47#define DTRACE_PROBE1(name, type1, arg1)
48#define DTRACE_PROBE2(name, type1, arg1, type2, arg2)
49#define DTRACE_PROBE3(name, type1, arg1, type2, arg2, type3, arg3)
50#define DTRACE_PROBE4(name, type1, arg1, type2, arg2, type3, arg3, type4, arg4)
51#define DTRACE_PROBE5(name, type1, arg1, type2, arg2, type3, arg3, \
52 type4, arg4, type5, arg5)
53#define DTRACE_PROBE6(name, type1, arg1, type2, arg2, type3, arg3, \
54 type4, arg4, type5, arg5, type6, arg6)
55#define DTRACE_PROBE7(name, type1, arg1, type2, arg2, type3, arg3, \
56 type4, arg4, type5, arg5, type6, arg6, type7, arg7)
57
58#ifdef KDTRACE_HOOKS
59SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt, , , set__error);
60
61#define SET_ERROR(err) \
62 ((sdt_sdt___set__error->id ? \
63 (*sdt_probe_func)(sdt_sdt___set__error->id, \
64 (uintptr_t)err, 0, 0, 0, 0) : 0), err)
65#else
66#define SET_ERROR(err) (err)
67#endif
68
69#endif /* _OPENSOLARIS_SYS_SDT_H_ */
